creator: FUTBASE
descriptionHtml:
Player Potentials 21 application has 9 different free filter options. With Overall Rating, Potential Rating, Age, Preferred Positions, Nationality, League, Club, Contract and Skill filters it is very easy to search and find players for your career mode team in FIFA 21 game. This application will be your biggest guide during the transfer seasons.

Also you can reach easily;
- Wonderkids,
- Hidden Gems,
- Highest Growths Players,
- Free Agent Players

You can save the players to your list with Favorite Players feature.

In Player Details page you can see very detailed data like Player Photo, Player Full Name, Preferred Positions, Preferred Foot, Day Of Birth, Height, Weight, Contract End Date, Wage, Value, Release Clause, Specialties, Traits, Weak Foot, Skill Moves, Work Rates and Player Ratings Per Positions.

The data base of the application is constantly updated with FIFA 21 game. If you want to follow the latest game data of FIFA 21, follow our application's updates.

If you like to play FIFA 21 game and also love football this app absolutely for you.


Disclaimer;
This is unofficial helper app for the game FIFA 21. Player Potentials 21 application has any relation to EA Sports companies. This app only provides FIFA 21 in-game footballer lists presented by its creators.
